WEBVTT

00:02:29.047 --> 00:02:31.427
This is a critical distinction,

00:02:31.451 --> 00:02:35.917
but it's not one that's emphasized
in the most elite oncology training.

00:02:36.774 --> 00:02:40.771
Instead, I was dismissed
with an appointment to start treatment

00:02:40.795 --> 00:02:42.487
in just a few weeks.

00:02:43.531 --> 00:02:47.185
So much has happened
since that first visit.

00:02:47.209 --> 00:02:50.459
Ironically, the biopsy was not
just a mere formality.

00:02:50.483 --> 00:02:53.514
My former oncologist was right.

00:02:53.538 --> 00:02:54.661
(Laughter)

00:02:54.685 --> 00:02:56.273
It did show cancer,

00:02:56.297 --> 00:03:00.237
but it was a totally separate lung cancer,